snippet.title: Neon Sword - #PitchYaGame - Trailer
snippet.description:
From Twitter:
#PitchYaGame 
Here's my game Neon Sword I've been working on it alone for a few years now it's an RPG with some business management aspects in the style of the old GTA's with a synthwave flavour.
